body:
And yeah, it feels bad, sure i got 5 shards, but they are all low IP champions, so low rolling really just means &quot;you got fucked, here is a bunch of champions you already own regardless of if your new&quot;

3X 90 BE shards
2X 270 BE shards

And now i know that even in the low roll of this system, it&#039;s not a matter of rerolling for the next shard, it&#039;s a matter of &quot;your getting the lowest possible shards no matter what.&quot;

But hey this system is totally designed to be &quot;awesome&quot; and &quot;fun&quot; and &quot;rewarding&quot;

Oh yeah and before i forget, one of the shards was Garen, and i&#039;m sure new accounts low rolling have a heavy chance of getting shards of champions that are FORCED ownership.
